                                                    Iridium Poised to Make Global Maritime Distress and Safety System History
                                                


                                                    GlobeNewswire – 
                                                    8:01 AM ET 07/11/2017
                                                


Iridium Communications Inc. (IRDM) announced today that two key milestones along the path to becoming the second recognized provider of Global Maritime Distress Safety System services have been reached.

















