Iridium Communications Inc. (IRDM), the only communications company with 100 percent global coverage, today officially launched Iridium Edge, its new, cost-effective global asset tracking, safety and fleet management device. Iridium Edge has already been approved for use in major global markets, including the United States, Canada, Europe and Australia with additional markets planned.

















